title: Albert King With Stevie Ray Vaughan - In Session (1983; 1999) [F
description:
In Session is a blues album by Albert King with Stevie Ray Vaughan recorded live for television on December 6, 1983, at CHCH-TV studios in Hamilton, Ontario, Canada, and released as an album on August 17, 1999.

    Tony Llorens : Piano, Organ
